    <h2>ğŸ¯ Daily Task Objective</h2>
    <p>Create a <strong>Health Expenditure & Outcomes Dashboard</strong> that addresses:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>ğŸ“Š How does per-person health spending vary across countries and over time?</li>
      <li>ğŸ’‰ Is there a measurable relationship between health spending and key outcomes (e.g., life expectancy, infant/child mortality)?</li>
      <li>ğŸŒ Where are the spending outliers â€” high cost, low outcomes or low cost, high outcomes?</li>
