      </li>
      <li>Calculate derived fields such as:
        <ul>
          <li>ğŸ” <strong>Spending Growth (%)</strong> = (current year spend - previous year spend) Ã· previous year spend</li>
          <li>ğŸ” <strong>Spend per Outcome Ratio</strong> â€” if merged with life expectancy or mortality data: <code>spend_usd Ã· life_expectancy_years</code></li>
