    <h3>3ï¸âƒ£ Build Your Dashboard</h3>
    <p>Use R (ggplot2/plotly/quarto), Python (matplotlib/plotly/dash), or Power BI to build visuals such as:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>ğŸ“ˆ Line Chart: Health spending per person over time by country or income group</li>
      <li>ğŸŒ Map: Global spending per person latest year (color-coded) and change over time</li>
      <li>ğŸ“Š Scatter Plot: Spending per person vs. life expectancy or other outcome (bubble size = population if available)</li>
      <li>ğŸ† Bar Chart: Top 10 countries by health spending per person, and bottom 10</li>
      <li>ğŸ“‹ KPI Cards: Average global spend per person, highest spending country, fastest growth country</li>
