    <p><strong>ğŸ’¡ Tip for Power BI:</strong> Use time slicer or animation for â€œyearâ€ to show how spending evolves.  
    <strong>ğŸ’¡ Tip for R/Python:</strong> Consider interactive dashboards using plotly or Shiny to allow filtering by region or income group.</p>

    <h3>4ï¸âƒ£ Add Key Metrics / KPI Cards</h3>
